close to equalize.}) 13. Qc2 Rd8 14. Rfd1 (14. a3 Bxd2 15. Nxd2 e5 $1 {and
Black equalizes:} 16. Nxc4 (16. dxe5 Qf5 $1 {is fine for Black, but not} (16...
Qxd2 $2 17. Rad1 $1 {and White wins.})) 16... Nxc4 17. Qxc4 exd4 18. Rfd1 d3
19. Rd2 Qe7 20. Qc3 c6 21. Rxd3 Rxd3 22. Qxd3 Be6 $11 {Halldorsson-Efremov,
